1
00:01:50,810 --> 00:01:52,835
What are you doing here?

2
00:01:53,646 --> 00:01:55,546
Yes... well, I'm...

3
00:01:55,748 --> 00:01:59,377
I was sent by the household
service agency to work here.

4
00:02:00,220 --> 00:02:01,983
Are you the new maid?

5
00:02:02,922 --> 00:02:03,820
What is your name?

6
00:02:04,757 --> 00:02:07,021
Y- Yes! My name is Maya.

7
00:02:16,936 --> 00:02:29,371
IMMA YOUJO

8
00:02:33,820 --> 00:02:35,720
Welcome back, Master.

9
00:02:35,955 --> 00:02:36,387
Oh?

10
00:02:39,058 --> 00:02:42,629
Tomoka, why don't you help
her change into her uniform.

11
00:02:42,664 --> 00:02:43,357
Y- Yes.

12
00:02:53,139 --> 00:02:55,334
Wow!

13
00:02:56,709 --> 00:02:58,438
Is this the bathroom?

14
00:02:59,279 --> 00:03:01,144
I'll leave your change of clothes here.

15
00:03:01,247 --> 00:03:02,380
This is gorgeous.

16
00:03:02,415 --> 00:03:04,975
I've never seen a beautiful bathroom like this.

17
00:03:05,418 --> 00:03:07,587
Hey, hurry up and go inside.

18
00:03:07,622 --> 00:03:09,756
I have other work to do.

19
00:03:09,791 --> 00:03:11,690
Oh, yes. I'm sorry.

20
00:03:12,058 --> 00:03:13,855
Please don't make a mess.

21
00:03:17,397 --> 00:03:18,596
I get excited too easily.

22
00:03:18,631 --> 00:03:20,462
It's a bad habit of mine... Oh well.

23
00:03:41,621 --> 00:03:42,815
This feels great.

24
00:03:43,156 --> 00:03:47,024
I can't believe I can work in such
a big mansion. It's like a dream...

25
00:03:47,860 --> 00:03:48,986
But...

26
00:03:51,130 --> 00:03:53,189
I'm not sure I can do well here.

27
00:03:56,069 --> 00:03:58,003
Hey! How long are you going
to take a bath in there?

28
00:03:58,204 --> 00:03:59,364
Y- Yes!

29
00:03:59,739 --> 00:04:01,138
I'll be out right away!

30
00:04:03,810 --> 00:04:04,435
Come in.

31
00:04:08,715 --> 00:04:09,875
I'm Maya.

32
00:04:10,083 --> 00:04:11,481
I'll do my best in your service.

33
00:04:11,516 --> 00:04:12,879
It's a pleasure to work for you.

34
00:04:13,219 --> 00:04:15,585
Thank you for coming in such heavy rain.

35
00:04:15,855 --> 00:04:18,323
If you have any questions, please ask Tomoka.

36
00:04:19,292 --> 00:04:21,522
Yes, thank you.

37
00:04:31,437 --> 00:04:36,397
Our master's business is importing
and selling art and furniture.

38
00:04:39,579 --> 00:04:41,012
This is the living room.

39
00:04:41,714 --> 00:04:45,241
There are many valuable pieces
of furniture and art here.

40
00:04:45,718 --> 00:04:48,414
Please use extra care when you clean this room.

41
00:04:48,488 --> 00:04:49,512
Right! Oh...

42
00:04:51,491 --> 00:04:54,221
This is the atelier for our master's son, Masao.

43
00:04:55,061 --> 00:04:57,859
Really, so he's an artist?

44
00:04:58,197 --> 00:05:01,401
Masao prefers to eat his meals in the atelier,

45
00:05:01,436 --> 00:05:03,164
so always be sure to bring them here.

46
00:05:04,270 --> 00:05:04,759
Right!

47
00:05:06,339 --> 00:05:08,364
This is a portrait of the master's late wife.

48
00:05:08,741 --> 00:05:10,538
Masao was the one who painted it.

49
00:05:11,244 --> 00:05:11,938
Um...

50
00:05:12,211 --> 00:05:14,042
How did she die?

51
00:05:14,180 --> 00:05:15,044
Dunno...

52
00:05:17,717 --> 00:05:19,480
This is the wine cellar.

53
00:05:20,620 --> 00:05:23,487
The master enjoys having wine at dinnertime,

54
00:05:23,589 --> 00:05:25,058
so be sure to bring him some.

55
00:05:25,093 --> 00:05:25,717
Okay!

56
00:05:25,958 --> 00:05:26,583
Huh?

57
00:05:27,427 --> 00:05:28,086
Don't!

58
00:05:28,261 --> 00:05:28,852
What?

59
00:05:29,329 --> 00:05:32,230
You can't go in here unless our
master gives you permission.

60
00:05:32,498 --> 00:05:33,192
Do you understand?

61
00:05:33,633 --> 00:05:35,123
I... I'm sorry.

62
00:05:36,235 --> 00:05:37,759
Well, come with me.

63
00:05:37,837 --> 00:05:38,735
Y... Yes!

64
00:05:40,073 --> 00:05:41,540
This is our room.

65
00:05:41,808 --> 00:05:43,776
I put your things over there.

66
00:05:44,377 --> 00:05:46,311
Oh, thank you very much.

67
00:06:06,232 --> 00:06:08,200
Umm... Master Masao?

68
00:06:11,471 --> 00:06:12,665
Leave it over there.

69
00:06:13,072 --> 00:06:14,733
Ah... o-okay!

70
00:06:31,524 --> 00:06:33,754
Maya, I brought warm milk for you.

71
00:06:34,026 --> 00:06:35,823
You can sleep well after you drink this.

72
00:06:38,231 --> 00:06:39,255
Thank you.

73
00:06:39,766 --> 00:06:40,664
It's really warm.

74
00:06:42,268 --> 00:06:43,860
And it tastes good!

75
00:06:44,637 --> 00:06:45,695
I'm glad you like it.

76
00:06:46,272 --> 00:06:48,502
I drink this every night.

77
00:06:48,808 --> 00:06:51,003
Let's drink together from now on.

78
00:06:51,878 --> 00:06:54,176
Can we? Wonderful!

79
00:08:36,649 --> 00:08:38,514
It's a nice day, Tomoka.

80
00:08:38,751 --> 00:08:40,412
It's hard to believe there
was so much rain yesterday.

81
00:08:42,154 --> 00:08:43,454
Be quiet...

82
00:08:43,489 --> 00:08:45,047
Please let me sleep a little more.

83
00:08:45,691 --> 00:08:46,248
Oh!

84
00:08:53,966 --> 00:08:55,763
Good morning, Master Masao.

85
00:08:57,036 --> 00:08:58,401
I'm Maya.

86
00:08:58,671 --> 00:09:01,936
Um... I brought your dinner
last night to your atelier.

87
00:09:05,344 --> 00:09:07,141
Oh, that's a beautiful flower.

88
00:09:07,513 --> 00:09:10,038
What is the name of this flower?

89
00:09:11,183 --> 00:09:13,617
I like flowers very much!

90
00:09:13,986 --> 00:09:16,716
Although, I don't know the
flowers' names very well.

91
00:09:17,423 --> 00:09:20,688
Butjust looking at them makes me very happy.

92
00:09:21,994 --> 00:09:24,258
Ah... Master Masao?

93
00:09:29,669 --> 00:09:31,068
Have a good day.
Have a good day.

94
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,947
I brought your meal.

95
00:09:44,150 --> 00:09:45,947
Um... Master Masao?

96
00:09:48,688 --> 00:09:51,555
So, this is an artist's room?

97
00:09:53,759 --> 00:09:55,283
I wonder what's inside this box?

98
00:09:55,795 --> 00:09:56,523
Don't touch!

99
00:09:58,931 --> 00:10:00,831
D- Don't touch it!

100
00:10:05,905 --> 00:10:07,236
M- Master Masao!

101
00:10:08,341 --> 00:10:10,309
I... I said don't touch this!

102
00:10:10,776 --> 00:10:12,505
I- I'm sorry!

103
00:10:28,361 --> 00:10:33,264
I'm planning to hold my next party
on the 15th of next month.

104
00:10:33,466 --> 00:10:36,958
Really? I think that's a good time.

105
00:10:37,970 --> 00:10:40,773
Anyway, how is your collection coming?

106
00:10:40,808 --> 00:10:42,104
It's coming well.

107
00:10:42,341 --> 00:10:46,835
I can't wait to show it in front of people.

108
00:10:50,383 --> 00:10:52,510
You sound very confident.

109
00:10:52,818 --> 00:10:55,116
Well, I look forward to seeing it.

110
00:10:58,224 --> 00:11:01,751
Master Masao, I brought your lunch.

111
00:11:02,995 --> 00:11:03,984
Master Masao.

112
00:11:17,476 --> 00:11:18,204
Maya.

113
00:11:22,515 --> 00:11:23,880
Welcome home.
Welcome home.

114
00:12:37,857 --> 00:12:39,051
Tomoka?

115
00:12:54,273 --> 00:12:56,798
I don't know why, but I feel dizzy.

116
00:13:37,516 --> 00:13:40,815
Rejoice Tomoka... It's time for your debut.

117
00:13:42,288 --> 00:13:46,987
The party is the 15th of this month.
I'm sure you will do well, Tomoka.

118
00:13:47,193 --> 00:13:49,593
No way... What is this?

119
00:13:51,630 --> 00:13:55,498
Tomoka... Mr. Hagiwara... and Master...

120
00:14:04,176 --> 00:14:06,804
Soon I think Maya will be
ready to prepare as well.

121
00:14:07,079 --> 00:14:09,604
I understand. Then I will
take care of it tomorrow.

122
00:14:09,748 --> 00:14:11,340
Do a good job, Tomoka.

123
00:14:21,560 --> 00:14:23,118
Maya, Maya!

124
00:14:26,332 --> 00:14:27,424
Tomoka.

125
00:14:28,534 --> 00:14:29,694
What is wrong with you?

126
00:14:29,969 --> 00:14:31,436
You seemed like you were having a nightmare.

127
00:14:33,239 --> 00:14:35,332
Tomoka... umm...

128
00:14:35,774 --> 00:14:36,502
