129
00:14:36,675 --> 00:14:38,700
No, it's nothing.

130
00:14:38,777 --> 00:14:39,903
You're acting strangely.

131
00:14:40,479 --> 00:14:42,845
I guess you must have had a scary dream.
Are you alright?

132
00:14:44,450 --> 00:14:46,748
Dream? Was that a dream?

133
00:15:00,332 --> 00:15:01,697
Have a nice day.
Have a nice day.

134
00:15:07,973 --> 00:15:08,667
Huh?

135
00:15:11,543 --> 00:15:14,307
Master Masao, I brought your meal.

136
00:15:15,214 --> 00:15:16,078
May I come in?

137
00:15:17,082 --> 00:15:18,947
I will leave your meal here.

138
00:15:40,739 --> 00:15:43,139
W- Well, if you'll excuse me.

139
00:15:46,412 --> 00:15:49,347
Hurry... and escape from here. Maya.

140
00:16:17,176 --> 00:16:19,610
You did a really bad thing, Maya.

141
00:16:20,846 --> 00:16:22,074
I'm very sorry!

142
00:16:22,982 --> 00:16:28,079
Of all the art, how could you break
the vase that Master liked the most.

143
00:16:28,787 --> 00:16:31,381
It's a foreign-made vase.
You can't get it in Japan.

144
00:16:32,558 --> 00:16:34,425
You could never pay it back,

145
00:16:34,460 --> 00:16:36,428
no matter how long you worked here.

146
00:16:37,796 --> 00:16:38,990
M- Master!

147
00:16:40,265 --> 00:16:42,165
I'm really sorry!

148
00:16:42,601 --> 00:16:46,401
Even though you apologize,
the vase can't be fixed.

149
00:16:47,172 --> 00:16:51,074
I'm sorry, I will do anything I can.

150
00:16:52,111 --> 00:16:53,601
Please forgive me!

151
00:16:54,380 --> 00:16:56,678
Maya, lift up your face.

152
00:16:58,150 --> 00:16:58,673
Yes...

153
00:17:01,754 --> 00:17:05,588
Will you do anything I say, Maya?

154
00:17:06,025 --> 00:17:08,391
Y... Yes...

155
00:17:09,194 --> 00:17:10,092
...Master.

156
00:17:21,173 --> 00:17:21,935
<i>Nd way...</i>

157
00:17:24,043 --> 00:17:26,273
No! Let me go! No!

158
00:17:26,945 --> 00:17:29,413
No, help me! Please!

159
00:17:40,059 --> 00:17:40,821
Tomoka.

160
00:17:41,093 --> 00:17:41,616
Yes.

161
00:17:49,368 --> 00:17:53,634
Maya, I will tell you what our real job is.

162
00:17:54,606 --> 00:17:59,305
The maids of this mansion will become
part of our master's collection.

163
00:18:00,779 --> 00:18:04,271
Maya, I will make you just like Tomoka.

164
00:18:04,783 --> 00:18:08,480
I will add you as part of my collection.

165
00:18:13,625 --> 00:18:17,755
First, I will show you the beauty
of my master's collection.

166
00:19:00,639 --> 00:19:02,266
Watch carefully.

167
00:19:02,374 --> 00:19:04,535
You will be just like that, soon.

168
00:19:08,113 --> 00:19:10,138
Don't be afraid.

169
00:19:10,349 --> 00:19:13,807
Maya, this will be your pleasure, too.

170
00:19:23,862 --> 00:19:26,228
Tomoka, why don't you do Maya next.

171
00:19:27,432 --> 00:19:27,989
Yes.

172
00:20:10,375 --> 00:20:11,899
Now I see...

173
00:20:12,578 --> 00:20:14,409
So, you are a virgin.

174
00:20:16,181 --> 00:20:18,479
Let's give this to our master now.

175
00:20:51,850 --> 00:20:53,613
No! Stop!

176
00:20:53,752 --> 00:20:55,845
No! No! Please don't!

177
00:20:59,558 --> 00:21:01,719
Here it comes, Maya!

178
00:21:01,793 --> 00:21:04,091
No!

179
00:21:29,955 --> 00:21:30,819
Maya...

180
00:21:31,023 --> 00:21:33,583
Master Masao, I brought your meal.

181
00:21:33,792 --> 00:21:34,850
I will leave it here.

182
00:21:49,975 --> 00:21:50,771
Maya!

183
00:21:54,212 --> 00:21:55,179
She's not here!

184
00:21:59,384 --> 00:22:00,146
Maya.

185
00:22:14,333 --> 00:22:15,800
How is it, Maya?

186
00:22:15,901 --> 00:22:19,359
I will make you into a
woman like Tomoka, soon.

187
00:22:20,272 --> 00:22:21,068
<i>Maya!</i>

188
00:22:29,081 --> 00:22:29,945
Damn it!

189
00:22:39,391 --> 00:22:43,225
You look beautiful, Tomoka.
Now it's time for you to debut.

190
00:22:44,062 --> 00:22:46,360
Thank you very much, Master.

191
00:23:01,580 --> 00:23:02,342
Maya.

192
00:23:05,550 --> 00:23:06,448
Maya!

193
00:23:21,666 --> 00:23:24,396
We can see Mr. Ayanokoji's
collection at the show tonight.

194
00:23:25,337 --> 00:23:26,565
I can't wait to see it.

195
00:23:27,739 --> 00:23:30,003
How did your collection come out?

196
00:23:30,208 --> 00:23:34,201
It came out great.
I'm sure you will be very satisfied.

197
00:23:35,013 --> 00:23:36,674
Well, it seems you have a lot of confidence.

198
00:24:41,046 --> 00:24:42,513
How do you like it?

199
00:24:43,949 --> 00:24:47,252
It's not bad, however...

200
00:24:47,287 --> 00:24:47,946
However?

201
00:24:51,990 --> 00:24:55,687
I got this from an importer the other day.

202
00:24:55,760 --> 00:24:58,964
I wanted to add a little
spice to your collection,

203
00:24:58,999 --> 00:25:00,431
so I brought them here.

204
00:25:14,646 --> 00:25:17,672
Master Masao... I... I...

205
00:25:19,918 --> 00:25:20,680
Maya.

206
00:25:23,655 --> 00:25:25,714
S... Stop that, Maya!

207
00:25:42,140 --> 00:25:46,201
The importer asked me to finance his company.

208
00:25:46,778 --> 00:25:47,978
I'm thinking about it.

209
00:25:48,013 --> 00:25:50,538
But I can't finance any more companies.

210
00:25:50,615 --> 00:25:52,382
So I've decided to make a deal...

211
00:25:52,417 --> 00:25:57,081
...with the company who has a better collection.

212
00:26:20,645 --> 00:26:24,137
<i>It's no good.
I can't take it anymore.</i>

213
00:26:24,449 --> 00:26:25,643
<i>Master...</i>

214
00:26:26,351 --> 00:26:28,444
<i>Master...</i>

215
00:26:45,170 --> 00:26:49,698
I thought your collection
could do a little better than this.

216
00:27:05,590 --> 00:27:08,320
Master Masao, I... I!

217
00:27:17,736 --> 00:27:18,896
You humiliated me, woman!

218
00:27:19,170 --> 00:27:21,263
You disgraced my name!

219
00:27:22,240 --> 00:27:23,366
Let's go, Hagiwara!

220
00:27:36,721 --> 00:27:40,680
Hagiwara, I will hold a party a week from now.

221
00:27:41,026 --> 00:27:41,515
What?

222
00:27:41,926 --> 00:27:43,723
I will debut Maya.

223
00:27:48,299 --> 00:27:49,231
This is great.

224
00:27:49,801 --> 00:27:51,098
It's very warm.

225
00:27:51,736 --> 00:27:53,727
I'm... I'm...

226
00:27:55,040 --> 00:27:58,009
I'll never let anybody take you, Maya...

227
00:28:16,027 --> 00:28:18,495
Masao! What are you doing?!

228
00:28:18,697 --> 00:28:19,561
Masao!

229
00:28:21,066 --> 00:28:21,794
Maya!

230
00:28:22,233 --> 00:28:24,997
Hagiwara, lock up Maya in the room.

231
00:28:26,104 --> 00:28:26,968
In one week,

232
00:28:27,739 --> 00:28:29,639
I will make Maya the best of my collection...

233
00:28:29,874 --> 00:28:33,241
...and prove to him what I can do!

234
00:28:35,480 --> 00:28:36,344
Maya!

235
00:28:36,514 --> 00:28:37,344
Shut up!

236
00:28:38,049 --> 00:28:38,947
No!

237
00:28:40,885 --> 00:28:43,615
Masao, stay in your room.

238
00:28:44,556 --> 00:28:48,014
Paint your pictures as usual, understand?

239
00:29:10,815 --> 00:29:15,149
Your wife has a nice one...

240
00:29:16,221 --> 00:29:21,420
All right, I think I can take care
of your company's financing deal.

241
00:29:23,228 --> 00:29:25,492
Thank you very much.

242
00:29:30,068 --> 00:29:31,501
Please don't cry, Mother.

243
00:29:31,603 --> 00:29:33,264
I will protect you.

244
00:29:36,474 --> 00:29:39,068
Mother!

245
00:29:54,726 --> 00:29:55,590
Mother.

246
00:29:56,261 --> 00:29:57,228
Mother.

247
00:29:57,762 --> 00:29:58,694
Mother.

248
00:29:59,330 --> 00:30:00,490
Mother.

249
00:30:04,469 --> 00:30:05,333
Maya.

250
00:30:05,870 --> 00:30:06,598
Maya.

251
00:30:06,805 --> 00:30:07,396
Maya.

252
00:30:07,672 --> 00:30:08,229
Maya.

253
00:30:08,673 --> 00:30:09,264
Maya.

254
00:30:09,741 --> 00:30:10,503
Maya!

255
00:30:11,009 --> 00:30:11,668
Maya!

256
00:30:11,943 --> 00:30:12,534
Maya!

257
00:30:12,811 --> 00:30:13,402
Maya!

258
00:30:13,645 --> 00:30:14,270
Maya!

259
00:30:14,479 --> 00:30:15,207
Maya!

260
00:30:15,380 --> 00:30:15,971
Maya!

261
00:30:21,052 --> 00:30:23,646
Please... Master.

262
00:30:24,155 --> 00:30:25,816
Please let me in.

263
00:30:26,624 --> 00:30:31,652
I feel crazy out here.
I will... Please!

264
00:31:14,205 --> 00:31:15,331
Are you ready, Maya?

265
00:31:46,638 --> 00:31:49,402
Now... Wake up, Maya.

266
00:31:49,908 --> 00:31:54,436
I put everything I know into you. Wake up!

267
00:31:55,179 --> 00:31:57,443
You are now reborn as a new woman, Maya.

268
00:31:57,782 --> 00:31:59,750
Maya... Maya!

269
00:32:08,293 --> 00:32:11,888
Welcome to my party, Count Mayuzumi.

270
00:32:12,230 --> 00:32:16,496
I brought my collection as you requested.

271
00:32:18,403 --> 00:32:20,200
Are you sure you want them to join?

272
00:32:20,305 --> 00:32:22,500
You may regret it.

273
00:32:24,008 --> 00:32:25,908
Please, don't worry about it.

274
00:32:41,726 --> 00:32:43,193
You look beautiful, Maya.

275
00:32:43,561 --> 00:32:46,758
I never expected you would
become such a beautiful woman.

276
00:32:47,832 --> 00:32:51,598
Master has put all his hopes on this party.

277
00:32:52,203 --> 00:32:56,105
Your debut is at such an important party...

278
00:32:56,674 --> 00:32:58,335
You must be happy, Maya.

279
00:32:59,777 --> 00:33:02,541
How prized a collectible have you become?

280
00:33:02,780 --> 00:33:05,180
I will taste you.

281
00:33:51,829 --> 00:33:56,289
Mother, they came here again.

282
00:33:56,834 --> 00:33:58,096
What can I do?

283
00:33:58,569 --> 00:34:01,732
They'll take Maya away from me now.

284
00:34:02,507 --> 00:34:04,168
But, I won't let them do that.

285
00:34:04,475 --> 00:34:05,942
Watch me, Mother.

286
00:34:45,216 --> 00:34:48,276
So, this is your new collection.

287
00:34:53,858 --> 00:34:56,019
I'm on my way, Maya.

288
00:35:22,854 --> 00:35:24,116
Well...

289
00:35:24,489 --> 00:35:25,421
How do you like it?

290
00:35:26,891 --> 00:35:29,155
It's getting very exciting.

291
00:35:49,680 --> 00:35:52,979
You might regret this, Ayanokoji.

292
00:36:16,774 --> 00:36:19,834
Let's see how long your collection will last.

293
00:38:14,725 --> 00:38:17,558
How do you like my Maya?

294
00:38:17,862 --> 00:38:22,424
If you like, I don't mind letting you have her.

295
00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:24,700
Really, Ayanokoji?

296
00:38:28,372 --> 00:38:30,499
Let's not play these silly games anymore.

297
00:38:30,741 --> 00:38:33,301
I found something more important than this.

298
00:38:34,312 --> 00:38:36,678
I want Maya. I need nothing else.

299
00:38:37,348 --> 00:38:39,942
I don't want money or status.
I only need Maya.

300
00:38:53,264 --> 00:38:56,097
Maya is mine!
Nobody can have her!

301
00:39:06,043 --> 00:39:06,600
What?

302
00:39:07,812 --> 00:39:08,676
Master Masao?

303
00:39:08,913 --> 00:39:12,212
Maya... I won't let anybody have Maya.

304
00:39:43,881 --> 00:39:47,214
I'm the one who should be standing there.

305
00:39:47,685 --> 00:39:49,846
Maya, if only you didn't come to this place...

306
00:39:52,356 --> 00:39:54,290
Don't, Tomoka!

307
00:39:54,558 --> 00:39:55,820
Maya!

308
00:40:12,743 --> 00:40:14,643
I will protect Maya.

309
00:40:18,749 --> 00:40:20,307
What are you doing here, Masao?!

310
00:40:23,621 --> 00:40:25,953
Nobody can stop me.

311
00:40:26,590 --> 00:40:30,754
Nobody can take Maya away.
Maya is mine!

312
00:40:51,515 --> 00:40:53,380
Maya is mine.

313
00:40:53,751 --> 00:40:56,117
Maya is mine!

314
00:43:26,203 --> 00:43:28,000
This is a wonderful collection.

315
00:43:28,372 --> 00:43:31,205
Would you please let me have him?

316
00:43:31,909 --> 00:43:35,208
Of course, I will pay you a desirable sum.

317
00:43:36,747 --> 00:43:38,247
Well, all right...

318
00:43:38,282 --> 00:43:41,513
...but only because the request
is from Count Tachibana's wife.

